# Pagecord

> Blog Without The Slog. Create your home page and blog in seconds.

Pagecord is a minimalist blogging platform for independent writers. Post by email or use the rich text editor. Free forever, premium plans available.

## Features
- Post by email (forward or compose to your blog)
- Rich text editor with images, tables, code blocks
- Custom home page
- Themes, colors, custom CSS
- Tags and RSS feeds
- Email newsletter (weekly digest or per-post delivery to subscribers)
- Privacy-respecting analytics
- Custom domains
- Reply by email (readers can respond to posts)
- Full site HTML export
- Dynamic open graph images

